9718da4f85","tid":590608,"uid":6703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"要返工搵錢已經無自由"},{"pid":"9a21a10c9453b72746c6573312a3059d410ce878","tid":590608,"uid":92095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"任何野去到極端都一定仆街"},{"pid":"ac7c258be461a2b95342d3253e415feebfbb0a09","tid":590608,"uid":90457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"每個群體已經注定有弱勢分子，適者生存，強者比弱者更自由係群居生物死症，冇底線嘅話其實意味著自由根本冇普及過<br />\n而強弱永遠係相對，強者經由唔受約束嘅自由剿滅弱者後，倖存嘅強-強者亦會消滅強-弱者，冇底線冇秩序嘅自由只會演變為獨裁<br />\n自由同平等似乎矛盾，但諗深一層兩者喺維護人權歷程根本一個都唔少得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d749078bd9f26fe481d6cc2c8ec5c1938b31ea0f","tid":590608,"uid":174231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf47b247ae70bcaed91a3f9f28ca80400776c1c","tid":590608,"uid":78163,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"除非你相信呢個世界有&quot;絕對&quot;呢回事，否則就係&quot;相對&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n自由亦都一樣，如果無&quot;絕對&quot;嘅自由，咁即係只有&quot;相對&quot;嘅自由 (意味著係有限制，而只差幾多限制而已)。"},{"pid":"059ff2e5b402cb7bc63b7d771edf82cdee7ee7ca","tid":590608,"uid":175322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"有選擇先有自由<br />\n我想做咩就做咩只係放縱，最後會失去埋真正既自由"},{"pid":"0790698986cbf2d2c65f0559f078092ffb1dcc90","tid":590608,"uid":100131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"港女: 我有派帽嘅自由<br />\n港男: 我有殺咗派帽女嘅自由<br />\n港女家人: 我有復仇嘅自由<br />\n港男家人: 我都有復仇嘅自由<br />\n港女親戚: 同上<br />\n港男親朋戚友: 同上<br />\n......咁loop?<br />\n<br />\n到時仲有無人敢同出街, 一個唔小心, 激嬲街上D廢老, 就要撕殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd45093a497976c01b41b96cdeeece060cc2419","tid":590608,"uid":169067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03cb12428802fc0a0a825f88ec986a5ba6e037be","tid":590608,"uid":174919,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T20:37:08.000Z","msg":"適當的底線能夠有效最大化自由<br />\n詳見社會契約論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"正義論"},{"pid":"f2392662792ce269e11f5b50ea965a063d7a66e7","tid":590608,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:53:27.000Z","msg":"自由係咪即係權利？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe38ddce1911e7d57629f0887d29b9131ce3bc31","tid":590608,"uid":112436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"其實呢個世界根本就係處於無底線嘅自由，你而家所謂嘅底線只係其他人用佢哋嘅自由定出嚟。你絕對有自由去推翻佢，但你有冇能力就係另一回事。"},{"pid":"5d90c1bda2c3a2b636216408df5dcafdbd473106","tid":590608,"uid":159274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T17:10:10.000Z","msg":"「自由」這個概念並不能獨立於「限制」而討論。<br />\n想像一下，最初當人類被拋擲到大地上，與一般動物無異。<br />\n當時我們還未為這個世界訂立「規則」／「法律」，我們可以為所欲為，做自己想做的事，甚至包括殺人。<br />\n但當時的我們並不會以「自由」來形容自己，因為我們覺得這一切是理所當然的。<br />\n例如我進食僅僅是因為我肚餓，並不是我行使進食的自由。<br />\n例如我殺人僅僅是因為發洩對對方的怨恨，並不是因為我行使殺人的自由。<br />\n但當人類為自己設限，我們才萌生出「自由」的概念，創造一種名為自由的價值，繼而追求自由。<br />\n所以限制（或是底線）是構成自由的元素。"},{"pid":"0f27d44f97b6e3ab430e1a340d495d8763d7fc26","tid":590608,"uid":152934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d14b47cba1296cc37e98055ff2c363626629b8f9","tid":590608,"uid":154131,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T20:48:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T18:31:39.000Z","msg":"定你老母義啦 一個transcendental idealism 搞掂你<br />\n最閪憎D定義撚完全沒有base premise 就係度講定義"},{"pid":"4fbe3fc4cf4bd1504bc4849f456cf0c4c3eb8509","tid":590608,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"個人認為自由有兩種：<br />\n<br />\n1.想打破受外界禁固既自由 擁有自己既意願同想法去行動 唔受環境他人限制<br />\n<br />\n2.自律即自由 遵從自己既思想行動 而唔係受原始既慾望控制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果底線係符合自己既價值觀既話 &quot;選擇唔去做一件事&quot; 喺思想上同行為上都係自由既一種 即係2.既自由<br />\n<br />\n但如果底線係別人 環境強加於自身 違背自己既意願既話 就唔係自由"},{"pid":"24a1df4a4c4ae599f26c021a3d0c3856805934ac","tid":590608,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"自由嘅終點線 就係人權嘅起步點"},{"pid":"ba9f06a618201b887dbcc7575961dc3c96e2bbbe","tid":590608,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"唔會有絕對自由"},{"pid":"78b47c11e78e9443fcd25bfd48fbc4cb756f57a1","tid":590608,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a1df4a4c4ae599f26c021a3d0c3856805934ac","tid":590608,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"自由嘅終點線 就係人權嘅起步點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"&quot;The liberty of the citizen ends where the liberty of another citizen begins.&quot;― Victor Hugo, Les Mis&eacute;rables<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Mais comme la libert&eacute; ne consiste qu'&agrave; pouvoir faire tout ce qui ne nuit ni aux droits d'autrui, ni &agrave; la s&ucirc;ret&eacute; publique, la loi peut &eacute;tablir des peines contre les actes qui.&quot;― Constitution de 1791"},{"pid":"b60d3b5cae412293d74b0767d73a0156b20d3dc3","tid":590608,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b47c11e78e9443fcd25bfd48fbc4cb756f57a1","tid":590608,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a1df4a4c4ae599f26c021a3d0c3856805934ac","tid":590608,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"自由嘅終點線 就係人權嘅起步點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"&quot;The liberty of the citizen ends where the liberty of another citizen begins.&quot;― Victor Hugo, Les Mis&eacute;rables<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Mais comme la libert&eacute; ne consiste qu'&agrave; pouvoir faire tout ce qui ne nuit ni aux droits d'autrui, ni &agrave; la s&ucirc;ret&eacute; publique, la loi peut &eacute;tablir des peines contre les actes qui.&quot;― Constitution de 1791"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T11:55:50.000Z","msg":"&quot;La libert&eacute; est le pouvoir qui appartient &agrave; l&rsquo;homme de faire tout ce qui ne nuit pas aux droits d&rsquo;autrui ; elle a pour principe la nature ; pour r&egrave;gle la justice ; pour sauvegarde la loi ; sa limite morale est dans cette maxime : Ne fais pas &agrave; un autre ce que tu ne veux pas qu&rsquo;il te soit fait.&quot;―D&eacute;claration des Droits de l&rsquo;Homme et du Citoyen de 1793 Article 6 (la libert&eacute;)"},{"pid":"78f80ce61bc5cc7582a4d57ba36bed74c07f0549","tid":590608,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:10:30.000Z","msg":"可以咁講，Civil liberty條底線應該係用嚟保障人嘅生存權、平等機會、私有產權等等，而唔係中意點定就點定。"}]}